{"tid":855451,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是日靚午餐 露絲瑪利大蒜粉香煎雞上脾 拼 炸洋蔥圈","createTime":"2018-10-10T05:06:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-11T06:12:56.000Z","uid":33359,"like":142,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"2b262b846812041ad3a6077c28f70ea1e77c0d9c","tid":855451,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T05:06:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/10/130641_87233a68f8c02e0af2aabba682ab98cd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F10%2F130641_87233a68f8c02e0af2aabba682ab98cd.png&h=5274fc75&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2597cdd62050016b086057856104a16c057ea5d9","tid":855451,"uid":201303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T05:07:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ac1f0b21291485f472a9dd343e0c414725cbea5","tid":855451,"uid":94662,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T05:07:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48490324b4866f0c3b8d21a6466d21110b7cbee1","tid":855451,"uid":113064,"like":60,"dislike":0,"score":60,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T05:07:53.000Z","msg":"一剔過<br />\nA、B、C、D餐係固定午餐<br />\n而E、F、G、H餐係每星期都轉一次<br />\n連埋蒜包餐湯凍飲 原價$45 / 48 / 50蚊<br />\n1230前埋單 / 1415後入坐減5蚊<br />\n盛惠$40 / 43 / 45蚊<br />\n推介菜式係皇牌燒雞 + 避風塘脆薯皇<br />\n星期六會送埋甜品 暫時係焦糖燉蛋<br />\n有緣仲會見到連登飲食台<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>堅硬台柱</strong></span><br />\n香港飲食評論<del><strong>打手</strong></del>界<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>超級巨星</strong></span></span><br />\n聲稱<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>中立非 _ _ (百搭<del>亂填</del>)</strong></span></span>嘅<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">慘過番印度</span></span><br />\n<br />\n百里香 觀塘駿業街67號熟食市場1樓44號<br />\n路線：港鐵觀塘站A2出口 步行約6分鐘<br />\n營業時間：一至五11:00-16:30；六11:00-16:00<br />\n外賣熱線：67082851<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">資料由<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">原創者</span>那吾克儉提供</span>"},{"pid":"1eee0e5b5fe48462e0c8b2f6f2a7320ea256c2c7","tid":855451,"uid":7521,"like":6,"dislike":34,"score":-28,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T05:08:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/10/130818_56921d51ab74d080fae39f80f59d95a5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F10%2F130818_56921d51ab74d080fae39f80f59d95a5.png&h=ce646c8f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7dbce05ecc18d49798f85a9f0a694db95b53aeb8","tid":855451,"uid":21423,"like":42,"dislike":18,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T05:08:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"64d76634be6086cc2cdf7d23e8562c54bb9d8f74","tid":855451,"uid":113064,"like":48,"dislike":0,"score":48,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T05:09:23.000Z","msg":"食得好過人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n影得靚過人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n果然係<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>中立非打手</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae426dd04bc376a328c4ae2452815f76a97d3e96","tid":855451,"uid":30694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T05:09:56.000Z","msg":"中非打"},{"pid":"e2ce6d2542bced6fa65a97ee181dd89806cb913d","tid":855451,"uid":135,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T05:10:51.000Z","msg":"尋日食左 點解我個洋葱圈冇你咁靚"},{"pid":"a5397f38e6df73ab34d815986100f4550be12928","tid":855451,"uid":33359,"like":31,"dislike":6,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T05:11:29.000Z","msg":"講下味道先<br />\n雞脾煎得外皮香脆 肉質都算嫩滑<br />\n可惜調味太淡<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n由其琴日食左佢個燴梅頭肉 好濃味<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"